      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i get that. but i've noticed a lot of the school staff and some of the other parents seem to imply that the people who are worried about it are just being \"anti-science\" or \"close-minded.\" i don't want to be that person, but i also feel like i have a right to be concerned about what's being taught to my kid. is there a legitimate basis for the concerns parents have, or is it mostly just based on misunderstanding the topic?",
